fields.name: Bora Bora
fields.description: I've always seen the majestic views of the water. I want to take my baby girl on a romantic getaway for a few weekends. Can't wait to share champagne and sunsets!

fields.name: Santorini
fields.description: The blue and white structures are so magical. Ideally this would be a dream honeymoon! Hint hint! But it's just a surreal place next to the waters.

fields.name: Rome
fields.description: After having travelled through Europe before, I want to see a place rich with history.  All roads lead to Rome, and one day I will get there too!

fields.name: Capetown
fields.description: I've traveled all over the world, but Capetown captivated my imagination. I want to experience a place and a culture that is far from the reaches of this sunny so cal girl.

fields.name: Rwanda
fields.description: Sharks and Gorillas are magical creatures. Rwanda is one of the few places left to see this endangered species. I can't wait to drag some of my best friends to see gorillas in Africa!

fields.name: Paris
fields.description: Paris is just a magical place. Love is always in the air in Paris. I want to get away and just forget the daily life just for a brief moment to enjoy life and its wonders.

fields.name: Bali
fields.description: My wife and I recently got married. Life is going to change for us with this married life, and I think Bali would be a great places to relax and enjoy the serenity of the island.

fields.name: Bangkok
fields.description: Culturally Bangkok has it all. The food, temples, and the people. I would love to take a flight to the islands to Koh Phi Phi as well!

fields.name: Barcelona
fields.description: Love the laid back culture in Barcelona. I want to visit all of Gaudis structures and catch a futbol game. If time persists, I might even take a short flight to Ibiza!

fields.name: Lisbon
fields.description: Lisbon shows multiple contrasts between the historical and modern, combining different cultures, trends and lifestyles.

fields.name: Machu Picchu
fields.description: The ancient fortress city of the Incas in the Andes Mountains, south-central Peru.
